- initial config

++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
git config --global user.name "Gregorio Bueno"
git config --global user.email "garbueno@gmail.com"
git config --global core.editor subl            <<<<<------------ Subline as Editor
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++

- how to verify

++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
GRBUENO-M-M0DZ:~ grbueno$ git config user.name
Gregorio Bueno
GRBUENO-M-M0DZ:~ grbueno$ git config user.email
garbueno@gmail.com
GRBUENO-M-M0DZ:~ grbueno$ git config core.editor
subl
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++

- verify all

++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
GRBUENO-M-M0DZ:~ grbueno$ git config --list
credential.helper=osxkeychain
user.name=Gregorio Bueno
user.email=garbueno@gmail.com
core.editor=subl
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++

- create a directory and initiate Git

++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
GRBUENO-M-M0DZ:Git grbueno$ pwd
/Users/grbueno/CISCO/Git
GRBUENO-M-M0DZ:Git grbueno$ git init
Initialized empty Git repository in /Users/grbueno/CISCO/Git/.git/
GRBUENO-M-M0DZ:Git grbueno$
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++

- Git creates a .directory under directory above

++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
GRBUENO-M-M0DZ:Git grbueno$ ls -al
total 8
drwxr-xr-x   4 grbueno  staff   136 Nov 20 12:30 ./
drwxr-xr-x  39 grbueno  staff  1326 Nov 20 12:25 ../
drwxr-xr-x   9 grbueno  staff   306 Nov 20 12:30 .git/    <<--------- Git directory
-rw-r--r--@  1 grbueno  staff   566 Nov 20 12:27 Tips     <<--------- Only file under Git monitored directory

GRBUENO-M-M0DZ:Git grbueno$ cd .git
GRBUENO-M-M0DZ:.git grbueno$ ls
HEAD		config		description	hooks/		info/		objects/	refs/
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++

- 1st file "Tips" is Untracked (not being monitored by Git)

++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
GRBUENO-M-M0DZ:Git grbueno$ git status
On branch master

Initial commit

Untracked files:
  (use "git add <file>..." to include in what will be committed)

	Tips

nothing added to commit but untracked files present (use "git add" to track)
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++

- adding this file to Git

++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
GRBUENO-M-M0DZ:Git grbueno$ git add Tips

GRBUENO-M-M0DZ:Git grbueno$ git status
On branch master

Initial commit

Changes to be committed:
  (use "git rm --cached <file>..." to unstage)

	new file:   Tips

++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++

- after modifying and saving this file 'Tips', Git notes that it was modified

++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++

